claim.claim-text:
A method of controlling an electronic product comprising a gas sensor configured to detect a target gas, the gas sensor comprising: a hydrogel support arranged to be discolored through reaction with the target gas, wherein the hydrogel support comprises dye provided to be discolored in response to a pH change upon reaction with the target gas, the method of controlling the electronic product comprising:
detecting a color of the gas sensor;
determining a concentration of the target gas based on the detected color;

and
determining a state of a target food based on a concentration of the target gas.
